name: Travel To The Future
description:
"Travel To The Future" is the first interactive work and mini games that I made for the nft collection.


we are now growing up in the midst of a more advanced era, where technology and human artificial intelligence have developed far.
I invite and describe through this work to further train skills and not be left behind by this rapid technological development.

This game is inspired by the game "Spacewar" by Steve Russel in collaboration with Martin Graetz in 1961s.
 
- Story and game design by Fluktss
- Music by Fraction
